rows.label: qst701911_msg0001
rows.name:
Maquia, was it? Please bring
that skilled pilot here.

rows.label: qst701911_msg0101
rows.name:
The six of them have
departed for Invidia.

rows.label: qst701911_msg0102
rows.name:
Let's trust that they will return
safely with the Dragon Incense.

rows.label: qst701911_msg0103
rows.name:
Adel-sama and everyone, please do
what you must for yourselves.

rows.label: qst701911_msg0104
rows.name:
Or perhaps it would be
wise to rest and wait.

rows.label: qst701911_msg0201
rows.name:
They came through for
us, just as I expected.

rows.label: qst701911_msg0202
rows.name:
Now please deliver that
Dragon Incense to Freja-san.
I'm counting on you.
